Name: Jura S8 Automatic Coffee Machine, Piano Black
Description:
"





Careful attention to detail definitely puts the stylish design of the S8 in a class of its own. The high-quality, grooved water tank with a handle made of real metal and the heavy, chrome-plated cup grille add subtle accents. With its clear cut, sculptural design, the stylish S line exudes quality and precision in every way. It combines the best of the compact class with elements of the premium segment, including a hint of the GIGA. The impressive range of specialties and the stunning result in the cup satisfy even the most demanding coffee connoisseurs. With just a simple touch on the 4.3"" high-resolution color touchscreen display, one of 15 specialties flows into the cup. 
Ultimate coffee quality thanks to the AromaG3 grinder and Pulse Extraction Process (P.E.P.®)
4.3"" high-resolution touchscreen color display with sophisticated operating concept for intuitive navigation 
Professional fine foam frotherG2 for either feather-light milk foam or hot milk 
One-Touch function for 15 specialties – from espresso to latte macchiato
Dimensions & More:
11” x 13.8” x 17.3”
22 Lbs
Made in Switzerland
Warranty:
 
This limited warranty covers your new JURA Automatic Coffee Machine for two years or up to 6,000 coffee brewings, whichever comes first.


"
Category: Home & Kitchen/Small Kitchen Appliances/Espresso Machines
